{"word":"βραδύς","slug":"βραδύς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βραδύς</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>slow</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>ἵπποι βάρδιστοι θείειν</el> <i>slowest</i> at running, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>β. λέγειν</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>βραδέως χωρεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of the mind, like <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>tardus</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>προνοῆσαι βραδεῖς</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>τὸ βραδύ</el> <i>slowness</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>βραδέως βουλεύεσθαι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of Time, <i>tardy, late</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}